    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">每一次空降，都是一次从零开始的文明速写。</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">在这片残酷星域，用枪火勾勒边界，用建筑铸就荣光。</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">你，准备好迎接这场星际征服了吗？</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324250/extras/abe45d0c691fd95fb8753237565aa260.avif?t=1771898045\" width=1500 height=500 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗以<u>高速“割草”射击为核心，<strong>融合Roguelike升级</strong></u>。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >敌人如潮涌来，你在闪避与射击中收集经验、即时升级，并从随机的强力能力中选择进化方向。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>每一局，你都能组合出独一无二的战斗风格</strong></u>——是召唤大军平推，还是化身重装堡垒，亦或是驾驭高科技武器炮台精准点杀，皆由你定。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324250/extras/4350914f8ba456e2f0dba98ab980f873.poster.avif?t=1771898045\" width=1170 height=654 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324250/extras/4350914f8ba456e2f0dba98ab980f873.webm?t=1771898045\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324250/extras/4350914f8ba456e2f0dba98ab980f873.mp4?t=1771898045\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324250/extras/d1207387ff854418eacaabfdcf5c0393.avif?t=1771898045\" width=1500 height=500 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗间隙，利用地图资源快速建造：是布局兵营爆兵，<u><strong>竖起炮塔巩固防线，还是升级科技解锁战场支援？</strong></u></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >所有建筑仅在本局生效，迫使你在防御、经济、攻击间做出精准取舍，<u><strong>打造独一无二的关卡内家园。</strong></u></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324250/extras/7691e1359f05b1e47cbc21c54ce0acc0.poster.avif?t=1771898045\" width=1170 height=656 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324250/extras/7691e1359f05b1e47cbc21c54ce0acc0.webm?t=1771898045\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324250/extras/7691e1359f05b1e47cbc21c54ce0acc0.mp4?t=1771898045\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324250/extras/4c03b4b7b1480a4d0b69c6fb8b572a62.avif?t=1771898045\" width=1500 height=500 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >开局选择的领主副官，定义了你的玩法根基。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择擅长稳扎稳打的“防御大师”，开局自带坚固堡垒？还是选择精通生物科技的“孢子王”，以廉价海量单位淹没敌人？</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每位副官都拥有<u><strong>独特的建筑树、单位库和核心加成</strong></u>，让重复攻关充满新鲜感。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324250/extras/de3f15911ab1d402bfb6d62374060a8d.poster.avif?t=1771898045\" width=1170 height=656 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324250/extras/de3f15911ab1d402bfb6d62374060a8d.webm?t=1771898045\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324250/extras/de3f15911ab1d402bfb6d62374060a8d.mp4?t=1771898045\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324250/extras/a6f2a97a6f47e682285af77ebf7eea6f.avif?t=1771898045\" width=1500 height=500 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏采用<u><strong>粗线条、高对比的美漫卡通手绘</strong></u>画风。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >粗犷的轮廓线让每个单位在混战中依然醒目，夸张的动态表现让爆炸与射击充满力量感，高饱和色彩则确保了战场信息的清晰可读。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324250/extras/a6ef003047aaa2ec897deda64d045cbf.poster.avif?t=1771898045\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324250/extras/a6ef003047aaa2ec897deda64d045cbf.webm?t=1771898045\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324250/extras/a6ef003047aaa2ec897deda64d045cbf.mp4?t=1771898045\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324250/extras/03ce4228cf8cec8203495082e49df23e.avif?t=1771898045\" width=1500 height=500 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏的永久成长线清晰聚焦于扩展你的战略选择。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过完成挑战，你将<u><strong>不断解锁造型、能力各异的新作战单位，并强化现有兵种</strong></u>的基础属性。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这意味着你的“玩具箱”会越来越丰富，后续征程中从补给箱获得部队将更具多样性与深度。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324250/extras/729ebd47cd51232ed5a7299572c39d4d.poster.avif?t=1771898045\" width=1170 height=656 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324250/extras/729ebd47cd51232ed5a7299572c39d4d.webm?t=1771898045\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324250/extras/729ebd47cd51232ed5a7299572c39d4d.mp4?t=1771898045\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
